app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at http://www.mdpi.com/1996-1944/11/6/923/s1, Figure S1: DSC curves for (a) PLA, (b) PLA/CS-EO, (c) PLA/BP-EO electrospun fibres, Figure S2: FEGSEM images of PLA/BP-EO fibres containing (a) 5.0% v/ v, (b) 7.5% v/ v, (c) 10.0% v/ v and (d) 15.0 v/ v of BP essential oil, Figure S3: Mass spectra of (a) linalyl acetate, (b) α-pinene, (c) limonene and (d) β-caryophyllene, Figure S4: Hansen space obtained using MATLAB software, and Table S1: Properties of the chemicals used in this study.
